==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-micro-.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Prefix===
[[Category:English prefixes]]
'''micro-'''

#Very small.
#:''micro-miniskirt''
#In the [[International System of Units]] and other [[metric]] systems of units, multiplying the [[unit]] to which it is attached by 10<sup>-6</sup>. Symbol: [[µ]] (''official''), mc (''unofficial'').
#:''microgram''
#*'''Note:''' The symbol mc is used in non-scientific contexts where readers might not understand the official symbol, [[µ]]. For example, on bottles of vitamin tablets, ''micrograms'' is often abbreviated to mcg.

====Etymology====
From {{Gr.}} ''mikros'', small.

